	<Title>
		Eye exam: Is a laser retina scan worthwhile?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		A laser retina scan can complement a traditional eye exam, but it&apos;s usually not necessary.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is a laser retina scan necessary? My optometrist offers the test, but I&apos;m not sure if I need it.
	</Question>
